>ID:<space><at>Value<openparen>Identifier.Artifact<closeparen>" }      ATTR_ACTION { "" "ID_number_FR" "SET_TO" "Num<u00e9>ro<space>INRP<space>:<space><at>Value<openparen>Identifier.Artifact<closeparen>" }      ATTR_ACTION { "" "Year_EN" "SET_TO" "Report<space>Year:<space><at>Value<openparen>Report<space>year<closeparen>" }      ATTR_ACTION { "" "Year_FR" "SET_TO" "Ann<u00e9>e:<space><at>Value<openparen>Report<space>year<closeparen>" }      ATTR_ACTION { "" "Desc_Static_EN" "SET_TO" "The<space>Canadian<space>Environmental<space>Sustainability<space>Indicators<space><openparen>CESI<closeparen><space>program<space>provides<space>data<space>and<space>information<space>to<space>track<space>Canada<apos>s<space>performance<space>on<space>key<space>environmental<space>sustainability<space>issues.<space>The<space>Air<space>pollutant<space>emissions<space>indicators<space>track<space>emissions<space>from<space>human<space>activities<space>of<space>6<space>key<space>air<space>pollutants:<space>sulphur<space>oxides<space><openparen>SOX<closeparen><comma><space>nitrogen<space>oxides<space><openparen>NOX<closeparen><comma><space>volatile<space>organic<space>compounds<space><openparen>VOCs<closeparen><comma><space>ammonia<space><openparen>NH3<closeparen><comma><space>carbon<space>monoxide<space><openparen>CO<closeparen><space>and<space>fine<space>particulate<space>matter<space><openparen>PM2.5<closeparen>.<space>Black<space>carbon<comma><space>which<space>is<space>a<space>component<space>of<space>PM2.5<comma><space>produced<space>by<space>combustion<comma><space>is<space>also<space>reported.<space><space>Sectoral<space>indicators<space>on<space>air<space>pollutant<space>emissions<space>from<space>the<space>oil<space>and<space>gas<space>industry<comma><space>transportation<comma><space>off-road<space>vehicles<space>and<space>mobile<space>equipment<space>and<space>electric<space>utilities<space>provide<space>additional<space>analysis<space>on<space>the<space>largest<space>sources<space>of<space>Canada<apos>s<space>air<space>pollutant<space>emissions.<lf><lf>For<space>each<space>air<space>pollutant<comma><space>the<space>indicators<space>are<space>provided<space>at<space>the<space>national<space>and<space>provincial<solidus>territorial<space>levels.<space>They<space>also<space>identify<space>the<space>major<space>sources<space>of<space>emissions<space>and<space>provide<space>links<space>to<space>detailed<space>information<space>on<space>air<space>pollutant<space>emissions<space>from<space>facilities.<space>The<space>Air<space>pollutant<space>emissions<space>indicators<space>are<space>intended<space>to<space>inform<space>Canadians<space>and<space>decision<space>makers<space>about<space>progress<space>made<space>towards<space>reducing<space>emissions<space>from<space>human-related<space>sources<space>of<space>air<space>pollutants<space>and<space>about<space>the<space>effectiveness<space>of<space>emission<space>reduction<space>measures<space>in<space>reducing<space>emissions<space>to<space>improve<space>ambient<space>air<space>quality<space>in<space>Canada.<space>Information<space>is<space>provided<space>to<space>Canadians<space>in<space>a<space>number<space>of<space>formats<space>including:<space>static<space>and<space>interactive<space>maps<comma><space>charts<space>and<space>graphs<comma><space>HTML<space>and<space>CSV<space>data<space>tables<space>and<space>downloadable<space>reports.<space>See<space>the<space>supplementary<space>documentation<space>for<space>the<space>data<space>sources<space>and<space>details<space>on<space>how<space>the<space>data<space>were<space>collected<space>and<space>how<space>the<space>indicator<space>was<space>calculated." }      ATTR_ACTION { "" "Desc_Static_FR" "SET_TO" "Le<space>programme<space>des<space>Indicateurs<space>canadiens<space>de<space>durabilit<u00e9><space>de<space>l<apos>environnement<space><openparen>ICDE<closeparen><space>rend<space>compte<space>de<space>la<space>performance<space>du<space>Canada<space><u00e0><space>l<apos><u00e9>gard<space>d<apos>enjeux<space>cl<u00e9>s<space>en<space>mati<u00e8>re<space>de<space>d<u00e9>veloppement<space>durable.<space>Les<space>indicateurs<space>sur<space>les<space><u00c9>missions<space>de<space>polluants<space>atmosph<u00e9>riques<space>portent<space>sur<space>les<space><u00e9>missions<space>de<space>6<space>principaux<space>polluants<space>atmosph<u00e9>riques<space>g<u00e9>n<u00e9>r<u00e9>es<space>par<space>l<apos>activit<u00e9><space>humaine<space>:<space>les<space>oxydes<space>de<space>soufre<space><openparen>SOX<closeparen><comma><space>les<space>oxydes<space>d<apos>azote<space><openparen>NOX<closeparen><comma><space>les<space>compos<u00e9>s<space>organiques<space>volatils<space><openparen>COV<closeparen><comma><space>l<apos>ammoniac<space><openparen>NH3<closeparen><comma><space>le<space>monoxyde<space>de<space>carbone<space><openparen>CO<closeparen><space>et<space>les<space>particules<space>fines<space><openparen>PM2<comma>5<closeparen>.<space>Le<space>carbone<space>noir<comma><space>qui<space>est<space>une<space>composante<space>des<space>particules<space>fines<space><openparen>PM2<comma>5<closeparen><comma><space>produit<space>par<space>combustion<comma><space>fait<space><u00e9>galement<space>l<apos>objet<space>d<apos>un<space>suivi.<space><space>Les<space>indicateurs<space>sectoriels<space>sur<space>les<space><u00e9>missions<space>de<space>polluants<space>atmosph<u00e9>riques<space>provenant<space>du<space>l<apos>industrie<space>p<u00e9>troli<u00e8>re<space>et<space>gazi<u00e8>re<comma><space>transport<comma><space>des<space>v<u00e9>hicules<space>hors<space>route<space>et<space>de<space>l<apos><u00e9>quipement<space>mobile<space>et<space>des<space>services<space>d<apos><u00e9>lectricit<u00e9><space><openparen>services<space>publics<closeparen><space>fournissent<space>une<space>analyse<space>suppl<u00e9>mentaire<space>des<space>principales<space>sources<space>d<apos><u00e9>missions<space>des<space>polluants<space>atmosph<u00e9>riques<space>au<space>Canada.<lf><lf>Pour<space>chaque<space>polluant<space>atmosph<u00e9>rique<comma><space>les<space>indicateurs<space>sont<space>fournis<space><u00e0><space>l<apos><u00e9>chelle<space>nationale<space>et<space>provinciale<solidus>territoriale.<space>Les<space>indicateurs<space>d<u00e9>terminent<space><u00e9>galement<space>les<space>principales<space>sources<space>d<apos><u00e9>missions<space>et<space>fournissent<space>un<space>lien<space>vers<space>des<space>renseignements<space>d<u00e9>taill<u00e9>s<space>sur<space>les<space><u00e9>missions<space>de<space>polluants<space>atmosph<u00e9>riques<space>attribuables<space>aux<space>installations.<space>Les<space>indicateurs<space>sur<space>les<space><u00c9>missions<space>de<space>polluants<space>atmosph<u00e9>riques<space>visent<space><u00e0><space>informer<space>les<space>Canadiens<space>et<space>les<space>d<u00e9>cideurs<space>sur<space>les<space>progr<u00e8>s<space>accomplis<space>pour<space>r<u00e9>duire<space>les<space><u00e9>missions<space>des<space>principaux<space>polluants<space>atmosph<u00e9>riques<space>attribuables<space><u00e0><space>des<space>sources<space>associ<u00e9>es<space><u00e0><space>l<apos>activit<u00e9><space>humaine<comma><space>et<space>sur<space>l<apos>efficacit<u00e9><space>des<space>mesures<space>de<space>r<u00e9>duction<space>des<space><u00e9>missions<space>pour<space>r<u00e9>duire<space>les<space><u00e9>missions<space>afin<space>d<apos>am<u00e9>liorer<space>la<space>qualit<u00e9><space>de<space>l<apos>air<space>ambiant<space>au<space>Canada.<space>Cette<space>information<space>est<space>rendue<space>disponible<space>aux<space>Canadiens<space>sous<space>plusieurs<space>formats:<space>cartes<space>statiques<space>et<space>interactives<comma><space>figures<space>et<space>graphiques<comma><space>tableaux<space>de<space>donn<u00e9>es<space>HTML<space>et<space>CSV<space>et<space>rapports<space>t<u00e9>l<u00e9>chargeables.<space>Voir<space>la<space>documentation<s